snippet.title: Steam Ages Dev Diary! - Plants vs. Zombies 2: Reflourished
snippet.description:
Join the PvZ2: Reflourished devs for a sneak preview at our brand new world - Steam Ages! Redone from PvZ2's Chinese version, our new take on this world will have you defending your brains from both directions!

Video edited by @Petrifying 

Chapters:

0:00 - Intro
0:58 - Steam Ages
1:24 - Demo Level
7:55 - Outro

All members of our dev team can be found here: https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/498237462108176388/1017515716150296657/9-1-2022_reflourishedcredits.txt

PvZ2: Reflourished Discord Server: https://discord.gg/ba9rC7QdKb
